snippet.textDisplay: Hello fazerug I I just wanted to let you know I'm a big fan and I've been watching you for about 3 years now. I've seen you reach some big mile stones not only that but your videos always seem to brighten my day up when I'm going through a tough time or when I'm having a bad day but yea I just wanted to say that I think you should take me on a 10,000$ shopping spree because I'm going through a tough time right now not having much money to buy any gifts for my siblings and mom nor my mom having enough money to pay Bill's we barley make enough to pay the rent and Bill's we dont have extra money at all are fridge is empty most of the time beside basic necessities we need to survive because that's all we have enough for once again I think you should pick me because I just want to spoil my three little siblings because they deserve it they never complain about anything we buy the cheapest of everything and where very humble about it also I want to buy close shoes etc for my mom because sheDeserves the world she's been through hell n back let me tell you that from her being physically abused by my father when i was  very young to us being evicted from our house a couple years back but somehow she found the strength and courage to keep pushing and we have a roof under our head and food on the table an close on our back even if its rice and beans on our plate for 5 days straight we love because we know what my mom goes through to put that on our table. We've have many great times to not everything is bad but right now where really struggling and a ten thousand shopping spree would get us out the mud right now I'd spend 5k on close and food for us and another 5k on a car because my mom has to walk 1.2 miles to work and back she's had alot of health problems her whole life and a car would help out alot getting her and my siblings places all in all I didn't want to make this to long but I hope I win it doesn't hurt to try right I love you faze rug and your a huge inspirationTo me and my family always showing positive attitude an all in all staying humble hope you have a good rest of your day/night an faze out ✌
